{
  "stem": "2578.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The reason why I did it was that I was hoping that maybe, because I was shipped out the next day, then, from my brother, maybe by sheer coincidence I would be sent to the same place where he was, and we will be together again.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But this never happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They sent-- they sent me to a camp-- to an area by the name of Eule--",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A little-- a little town in-- in southern-- [INAUDIBLE] in the southern Silesia, in the German part on the-- part of Germany, close to the Polish border.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was there for about three weeks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, they sent me to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- the work consisted that a group-- the-- the group of peop-- of inmates that worked in this area consisted of a few groups.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- we were split up in groups.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One was chopping down trees.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Another group would clean the-- the branches from the trees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my-- my group, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we would carry these trees from one area-- from this area where it was-- where the-- from the area that they were cleaned to a-- to another place and drop them.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And come back and pick up another one, and take them there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were about-- we were allowed about six, seven men to carry a tree.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And after living under the most horrible conditions in the Lodz ghetto, starving for four years, freezing, being sick, swollen, and so on, you can imagine, we were skin and bones.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had to carry on our shoulders these trees.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Within after the first half hour, the skins were ripped off from our bones, here, from the shoulders.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, on top of it, we had to carry those trees.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You can imagine how we felt about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
